{"tid":1027993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【滙控放榜】香港續撐業績 全年稅前多賺近兩成 歐洲蝕 北美盈利減弱","createTime":"2019-02-19T07:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T02:25:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee7768e69a8aad255a4ddc686460b7ec7074cf4","tid":1027993,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"滙控（005）業績繼續由亞洲帶動。按列賬基準計，除稅前盈利按年多賺13.69%，至198.9億美元，亞洲貢獻近九成！<br />\n<br />\n亞洲稅前盈利按年增16%，錄177.9億美元，佔集團稅前盈利的89.5%，比率按年升0.2個百分點。歐洲、中東及北非業績均有改善，其中，歐洲稅前蝕8.15億元，虧損已較2017年少10.49億美元。不過，北美、拉丁美洲盈利能力減弱，累計對集團稅前盈利佔比大降6個百分點，至6.8%。<br />\n<br />\n香港繼續是滙控的福地，全年稅前多賺19.9%，至115.14億美元；中國全年稅前多賺14.87%，至28.58億美元。正如管理層在業績提到，去年末季收入受市場波動所影響而下降，香港去年第四季稅前盈利按季跌16%，至25.61億美元；中國第四季稅前盈利錄5.65億美元，按季跌23.85%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190219/59277062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F59277062&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=f7cf7a62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F59277062&h=061d68c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190219/59277062</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恭喜香港員工完成階段性任務"},{"pid":"2729f12c72d7716398774488f7c7a3572d155a74","tid":1027993,"uid":77196,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"獅王冇香港+個仔頂住，真係食得屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係對香港人D態度惡劣到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd941e672d8a46e5b12442e0748cc1c40b427141","tid":1027993,"uid":8439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"re